Model

Class GameObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • Model.GameObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MovableObject, Racket, StillObject

    public abstract class GameObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Main class of the game. Every object inherits from this class. Contains basic fields, which are required to properly draw and calculate place of objects collision, e.g. x and y coordintes, width, height, bounds. x and y indicate the upper left corner of object.
    Author:
    Antek
    See Also:
